title: Estadio Alsacias
text: Estadio Alsalsias is a <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> <a href="stadium">stadium</a> in <a href="La%20Entrada">La Entrada</a>, <a href="Honduras">Honduras</a>. It is currently used mostly for football matches and is the home stadium of <a href="Olimpia%20Occidental">Olimpia Occidental</a>. The stadium holds 2,000 people.
